<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">هـ ن د ب:</span> <span class="c2">(هِنْدَبٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(هِنْدَبَا)</span> بِالْقَصْرِ وَ <span class="c2">(هِنْدَبَاةٌ)</span> بِفَتْحِ الدَّالِ فِي الْكُلِّ بَقْلٌ.<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ أَبُو زَيْدٍ:</span> <span class="c2">(الْهِنْدِبَا)</span> بِكَسْرِ الدَّالِ يُمَدُّ وَيُقْصَرُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>